name: The Gates of Mogosoaia Palace
description: A beautiful red-haired woman looking at the gates of Mogosoaia Palace. The palace was built in 1702 and is located near Bucharest, Romania.  The girl in the photo is a dear friend of mine who has been having a rough time.  Any proceeds generated from this sale will be donated to her to fund medical bills.  Image information: 3200x5000.  ISO 1600, F2.8, 1/60
